    "discriminators": [
     "'Popping liquidy mud sounds.' The DARK counterpart of FIRE-CRACKLE: sparse, high-crest impulses, but with spectral_centroid_hz an order of magnitude LOWER and high_band_energy near zero. A dry wood snap is bright; a mud glop is a damped low-frequency cavity resonance. That band ratio is the real separator.",
